Introduction
------------
This Free application will import data and analyze the risks for only one AWS Account. 
Buy Saviynt's Premium Application for Splunk to import and analyze data for multiple AWS Accounts.
Refer to the User Guide on Splunkbase for more Information.

Installation
------------
Describe how to install your application here (if applicable).

Usage
-----
Click on "Import Data" tab and enter the credentials. Then click on "Yes" to import the data. 
You can also Click on "Reevaluate Risks" on homepage to re-import the data.
Refer to the User Guide on Splunkbase for more Information.

